data.title: 6abc Action News - WPVI Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, New Jersey and Delaware News
data.meta_description: Action News and 6abc.com are Philadelphia's source for breaking news and live streaming video online, covering Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, New Jersey, Delaware.
data.text:
What is our area?

Our area is our station's Demographic Area and contains the following counties.

Pennsylvania: Berks, Bucks, Chester, Delaware, Lancaster, Lehigh, Montgomery, Northampton, Philadelphia

Delaware: Kent, New Castle
